config CAVAN_SENSOR_BMI160
    tristate "bmi160 acceleration and gyroscope sensor support"
    default n
    help
      Say Y here if you have Bosch Sensortec's BMI160
      acceleration and gyroscope sensor hooked to an I2C bus.

